1981;;...All the Marbles;;American;;Robert Aldrich;;Peter Falk;;comedy, drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/...All_the_Marbles;;Harry is the manager of a tag team of gorgeous lady wrestlers. On the road, they endure a number of indignities, including bad motels, small-time crooks and a mud-wrestling match, while trying to reach Reno for a big event at the MGM Grand.